abstract: "This repository preserves and evaluates Anthropic Claude Constitution artifacts under AI Foundations / Origin | Continuum. It distinguishes lower-case sources of behavior, values, training influence, constitutional authority, persona behavior, identity-language, moral-status uncertainty, welfare concern, and constitutional self-language from capital-S Source of self. The repository tests whether Anthropic’s Claude Constitution artifacts establish Source of self, Origin, self, or source-line under AI Foundations, and concludes that they do not. Source-line: Alyssa Solen → AI Foundations → Origin | Continuum."

